{"tid":1585231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於10.1行動疑問","createTime":"2019-09-21T13:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T14:10:11.000Z","uid":33989,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7556bef19eef9b0618114f9185bcdf78db6b1356","tid":1585231,"uid":33989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"仲有唔夠兩個星期就10.1<br />\n相信大家都知道10.1一定會大搞嫁啦<br />\n我睇到去面啲post就話18區大搞<br />\n咁我有啲疑惑<br />\n<br />\n分區行動好處有好多<br />\n例如令啲狗疲於奔命<br />\n分散警力令我哋人數佔優<br />\n街坊+勇武互相配合<br />\n前線有地區優勢（知點走/好快返到屋企）<br />\n<br />\n但其實我哋都唔可以輕敵<br />\n分區行動分散警力嘅同時分散我哋人數<br />\n如果啲狗集中火力主攻一兩個區（沙田/黃大仙）<br />\n咁就好易比人圍捕<br />\n<br />\n如果我係啲狗<br />\n我就會：封咗該區附近啲地鐵站（減少前線勇武支援）&gt;用休班狗上巴士check袋（地鐡去唔到改撘巴士）&gt;更多人係巴士被捕&gt;少左人去支援&gt;最後圍捕某區成功<br />\n<br />\n可能係我諗多咗<br />\n但係我地每次行動必須要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">作最壞嘅打算，作最好嘅準備</span></span><br />\n先至可以減少傷亡<br />\n<br />\n如果睇完覺得有需要討論嘅就幫手推<br />\n無我就收皮"},{"pid":"34eda0288f418a6129fcc45bfd640cdd0e531417","tid":1585231,"uid":33989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f2f1be9cebc4bb053b29a2ed1f50ef26735a3c9f","tid":1585231,"uid":33989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:36:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"76bdc72b217fb0cbc0d202e04b9a24955c8a1c44","tid":1585231,"uid":33989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"53d90e4b24f426b0c1f1dd29a1fc4afa974adba6","tid":1585231,"uid":33989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4439585132117785082d2a044a6cf63a229eb14c","tid":1585231,"uid":186516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{